{"lemma":"مَجْمَعَيْ","slug":"مَجْمَعَيْ","root":"ج.م.ع","root_slug":"ج-م-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-م-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"مَجْمَع","root":"جمع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6326","n6329"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%AC%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a junction (place where two or more things meet)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"assembly or congregation","examples":[{"text":"مَجْمَع نِيقْيَة","english":"Council of Nicaea"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"synod","examples":[{"text":"المجمع المقدس (للكنيسة القبطية الأرثوذكسية)","english":"Holy Synod (of the Coptic Orthodox Church)"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"shopping mall"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"college"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"academy"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Noun of place from the verb جَمَعَ (jamaʕa, “to bring together”).\n\nNoun of place from the verb جَمَّعَ (jammaʕa, “to collect, to gather”)"},"ipa":["/mad͡ʒ.maʕ/","/mu.d͡ʒam.maʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6326","headword_ar":"مَجْمَعٌ","root":"jmE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majomiEN","text_ar":"مَجْمِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) the latter anomalous, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$oriqN","text_ar":"مَشْرِقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magoribN","text_ar":"مَغْرِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place of collecting, and the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, * K:) [pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majaAmiEu","text_ar":"مَجَامِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majomaEu AlbaHorayoni","text_ar":"مَجْمَعُ البَحْرَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xviii. 59], means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The place where the two seas meet."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd.) And in like manner, where it is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fDaraba biyadihi majomaEa bayona EunuqiY","text_ar":"فضَرَبَ بِيَدِهِ مَجْمَعَ بَيْنَ عُنُقِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wakatifiY","text_ar":"وَكَتِفِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", [in which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA","text_ar":"مَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"seems to have been dropped by the copyist between"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mjmE","text_ar":"مجمع"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"byn","text_ar":"بين"},{"kind":"text","text":",] the meaning is, ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And he struck with his hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the place where my neck and my shoulder-blade meet."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [Hence also the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majaAmiEu AlmaHaAmidi","text_ar":"مَجَامِعُ المَحَامِدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", explained above: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAmiEN","text_ar":"جَامِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", near the end of the paragraph. And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majaAmiEu AlA^umuwri","text_ar":"مَجَامِعُ الاُمُورِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The concurrences of affairs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of circumstances,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of events."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place in which people collect, assemble,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"congregate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, * TA:) and [in like manner,] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majomaEapN","text_ar":"مَجْمَعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an assembly-room; a sitting room in which people assemble:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [pl. of both"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"majaAmiEu","text_ar":"مَجَامِعُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA AlkalaAmu A^awolaju fiY","text_ar":"هٰذَا الكَلَامُ اَوْلَجُ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmasaAmiEi waA^ajowalu fiY AlmajaAmiEi","text_ar":"المَسَامِعِ وَاَجْوَلُ فِى المَجَامِعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This language,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discourse, is more,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most, penetrating into the ears, and more,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most, circulating in the places of assembly"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamoEN","text_ar":"جَمْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAEapN","text_ar":"جَمَاعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places; and see 10, first sentence. ―         -b4-  [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whole"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything, considered as the place in which the several parts thereof are collected: see an instance voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuf~N","text_ar":"خُفٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mujotamaEN","text_ar":"مُجْتَمَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n6329","headword_ar":"مِجْمَعٌ","root":"jmE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jam~aAEN","text_ar":"جَمَّاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}